title: #157:The Chaos Of Broward County With Brendon Walsh
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another fun festive episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome comedian Brendon Walsh to the show to discuss all the bizarro stuff that seems to come out of Broward County, Florida! I appreciate all the support.
